Package com.github.games647.scoreboardstats.variables

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Replaceable Deprecated
    not fully featured and returns magic values.
    VariableReplacer
    Represents a replacer to update display names or integer values of the scoreboard.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LegacyReplaceWrapper
    Represents a wrapper in order to support the usage of the old Replaceable
    PluginListener
    Keeps track of plugin disables and enables.
    ReplaceEvent
    Represents a variable replace action
    ReplaceManager
    Handling the replace management
    ReplaceWrapper
    Represents a wrapper to support the usage of the interface instead of the VariableReplaceAdapter
    VariableReplaceAdapter<T extends Plugin>
    Represents a variable replacer as an abstract class.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    UnknownVariableException
    Represents an exception if a used variable can't be replaced by a replacer So if no replacer know this variable
    UnsupportedPluginException
    Represents an exception if the plugin isn't supported by a replacer.
